- EVERY page in the app MUST be 100% mobile responsive
- You must review every page and component to confirm all necessary design and styling requirements to make each page fully responsive has been implemented.
- Perform tests to confirm mobile responsiveness of pages and their elements
- Maintain WCAG contrast ratio standards for ALL fonts against their backgrounds in the app.
